HEADWORD: Fiendish
<hw>Fiend"ish</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Like a fiend;
diabolically wicked or cruel; infernal; malignant; devilish;
hellish.</def> -- <wordforms><wf>Fiend"ish*ly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos> --
<wf>Fiend"ish*ness</wf>, <pos>n.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Fiendlike</ent>⟦br⟧
